  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><span>Buffet breakfast, and 3-course evening meals with a choice of main course, occasional salad buffet, and weekly special themed dinners. A 5 course gala dinner is included on New Year’s Eve. </span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p class="p1">Hotel Krone enjoys a prime location in the heart of Oberperfuss, and combines the best traditions of Tyrolean quality and friendly hospitality with bright, modern interiors and comfortable en suite bedrooms. As you see from our photos, the hotel comprises two wings, which are internally linked for guests’ convenience. There is a comfortable lobby/lounge area, a bar in which to relax after skiing, plus a separate stylish lounge-bar for an apéritif before enjoying the hotel’s excellent dining each evening. The wellness area and a bowling alley complete the hotel’s après-ski facilities. </p>
<p class="p3">Access to the skiing is easy, with a stop for the free ski-bus just outside the hotel, for the short approx. 5-minute ride to/from the main gondola-lift. There is free ski storage (not boots) at the Beginners’ Ski Area at the top of the gondola lift.</p>]]></description>
